In [[Gnosticism]] and [[Demonology]] '''Sananel''' was a former chief of the [[Heavenly host|angelic host]] who later became the [[demiurge]] or creator of the material world, and known as [[Satan]]. In some accounts he was the elder brother of Jesuel (the heavenly [[Jesus]]).

